div.p:
Having regard to its resolutions of 14 November 1947
(112(II)), of 12 December 1948 (195(III)), and of 21 October 1949 (293
(IV));

Recalling that the essential objective of the
resolutions of the General Assembly referred to was the establishment of a
unified, independent and democratic Government of Korea;

Mindful of the fact that at the end of the present
hostilities the task of rehabilitating the Korean economy will be of great
magnitude;

5. Expresses its appreciation of the services rendered
                        by the members of the United Nations Commission on Korea in the performance
                        of their important and difficult task;
